ernational Conference, ICCCI 2009, Wroclaw (Poland) 10.2009, in N.N. Than, K. Ryszard, C. Shyi-Ming (a cura di), ''Computational Collective Intelligence'', Semantic Web, Social Networks and Multi-agent Systems, Springer, Berlin-Heidelberg-NY 2009, pp.&nbsp;22–35. * Id., ''Algebraic Structure of IEML Semantic Space'', CI Lab Technical Report, 2009.
